[Item World Current Floor]
author=bungholio
description=Even if you skip to level 100 and win when you were supposed to be on the first floor, going back into the item will go to level 2. The levels are ?? - 1. 00 would be floor 1, 01 is floor 2, 02 is floor 3, 63 is floor 100.
patch=1,EE,002F65D4,extended,000000BE

